# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:13
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_ee474ea1:

    # "In English class, Mrs. McGee has us working on our essays in class again."
    "Na aula de Inglês, a Sra. McGee pede-nos para trabalharmos nas nossas redações novamente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:14
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_aaf24ec9:

    # "She walks around the room answering questions from any students and looking over their essays."
    "Ela anda pela sala a responder a perguntas dos alunos e a rever as suas redações."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:17
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_420a4be4:

    # "When she comes over and stands close to me, I freeze and stop writing what I was working on, all other thoughts drifting out of my head."
    "Quando ela se aproxima e fica perto de mim, fico paralisado e paro de escrever o que estava a fazer, com todos os outros pensamentos a desaparecerem da minha cabeça."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:20
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_35f4dc88:

    # "She touches her hand gently against my back."
    "Ela toca-me suavemente nas costas com a mão."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:21
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_b00da5b8:

    # et "It's okay, keep writing. I'm just reading what you have so far."
    et "Não faz mal, continua a escrever. Só estou a ler o que já escreveste até agora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:22
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_ab6d893a:

    # "I try to keep writing, but I can't think of anything else besides her touch."
    "Tento continuar a escrever, mas não consigo pensar em mais nada além do toque dela."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:25
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_e8652fd7:

    # "Then she leans down and whispers in my ear."
    "Então ela inclina-se e sussurra-me ao ouvido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:26
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_3a804160:

    # et "You're doing great."
    et "Estás a ir muito bem."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:27
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_17560636:

    # et "Your essay is looking really good."
    et "A tua redação está a ficar muito boa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:28
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_8c2b661c:

    # et "I can't wait to read the rest of it."
    et "Mal posso esperar para ler o resto."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:29
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_e41d9ed8:

    # "It's amazing how she is able to make me hard just by her proximity, just by her breath near my ear."
    "É incrível como ela consegue deixar-me excitado só pela sua proximidade, só pelo seu hálito perto do meu ouvido."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:30
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_de8b0af2:

    # "She doesn't have to say anything sexy. Her very nature exudes sex."
    "Ela não precisa de dizer nada sensual. A sua própria essência exala sensualidade."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:33
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_b37c130b:

    # "She continues walking around the room, but I notice her looking over at me more often than she did the other students."
    "Ela continua a andar pela sala, mas reparo que olha para mim com mais frequência do que olhava para os outros alunos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:34
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_54c6164b:

    # "I wonder if she is attracted to me like I am attracted to her."
    "Será que ela se sente atraída por mim como eu me sinto atraído por ela?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:35
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_dd91d32c:

    # "Because God, I want to fuck her so bad."
    "Porque, meu Deus, quero tanto foder com ela."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:36
translate portuguese mrsmcgee1_f21fec0a:

    # "Eventually the day ends, and I leave school to go to work."
    "Por fim, o dia acaba e saio da escola para ir trabalhar."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:2
    old "You have finished your English Homework."
    new "Terminaste o teu trabalho de casa de Inglês."

    # game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee1.rpy:3
    old "Mrs. McGee will be pleased with your efforts the next day of class."
    new "A Sra. McGee ficará satisfeita com o teu esforço na próxima aula."

